  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You brandish the weapon used in the spell's casting and make a melee attack with it against one creature within the weapon's reach. On a hit, the target suffers the weapon attack's normal effects, and you cause venom to seep from the wound. The target takes an additional <strong>1d4 poison damage</strong>, and if the attack was a critical hit, the target is poisoned until the end of its next turn.</p><p>This spell's extra poison damage increases by 1d4 when you reach 5th level (2d4), 11th level (3d4), and 17th level (4d4).</p>",
